2014年3月6日：&quot;ConsumptionStructureEvolutionsinanAgingSocietyandImplicationsfortheSocialSecuritySystem&quot;,&nbsp;PRI-ADBIConferenceon&quot;StrategiesforMaintainingFiscalSoundnessinAgingSocieties&quot;,Tokyo.
